  "sections": {
    "Background": {
      "text": "Gram negative\n, non spore forming bacteria\nCommonly found in animal feces\nCaused by oral-fecal transmission\nAssociated with\nGuillain-Barre syndrome\nand\nReiter syndrome\nIncubation period of about 2-5 days, with duration of illness around 2-10 days\n[1]",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
