        }
      ]
    },
    "Differential_Diagnosis": {
      "text": "Infectious:\nSalmonella\nShigella\nShiga toxin-producing\nE. coli\nE. coli\n0157:H7\nEntamoeba histolytica\nYersinia\nVibrio\nC. difficile\nNon-infectious:\nInflammatory bowel disease\nGI bleed\nAdrenal insufficiency\nMesenteric ischemia\nThyroid storm\nToxicologic exposure\nRadiation syndrome",
